  "purpose": {
    "summary": "This BMS map defines the screen layout for the CardDemo Pending Authorization screen. It displays customer account information, credit and cash limits/balances, and a list of recent transactions with their details (ID, date, time, type, approval status, and amount). The screen allows users to search for an account ID and select a transaction for further action.",
    "business_context": "This screen is used to view and manage pending card authorizations within the CardDemo application.",
